title: Student Rental  Waterfront
description: Waterfront house only  minutes to URI. House rents weekly in the Summer, in the winter home has been rented by URI students. It is 3 Bedroom ranch with two living rooms. The home has a new heat pump (mini split) that provides economical heat and ac. In the dead cold of winter the electric bill was $300. which is cooking, heat and hot water. All furnishings are included right down to the TV, plates pots etc. Just bring your cloths, sheets and towels.  The home looks out at Jamestown and is right on the water. You will have use of the large flat yard and fire-pit. This is a link to our website the rates you see there are for the summer weekly rental. There are plenty of pictures and a live cam of the view on the website.
